\c 53
\s Vanhu vese vakashata
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. NeMaharati. Masikiri. \add Pisarema\add* raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Benzi rakati mumoyo maro: Hakuna Mwari\x + Map. 14.1-7.\x*. Vakaodza, vakaita uipi hunonyangadza; hakuna anoita zvakanaka\x + VaRom. 3.10-12.\x*.
\v 2 Mwari wakatarisa pasi ari kumatenga pamusoro pevanakomana vevanhu, kuona kana pane anonzwisisa, anotsvaka Mwari\x + VaRom. 3.10-12.\x*.
\v 3 Umwe neumwe wavo\x + VaRom. 3.10-12.\x* wakadzokera shure; vakasvibiswa pamwe chete\x + Map. 35.4.\x*; hakuna anoita zvakanaka, hakuna neumwe.
\v 4 Vaiti vezvakaipa havana zivo here? Avo vanodya vanhu vangu \add se\add*vanodya chingwa. Havadani Mwari\x + Map. 94.4.\x*.
\v 5 Ipapo vaitya zvekutya, pasina chinotyisa\x + Rev. 26.17.\x*; nokuti Mwari\x + Map. 14.5.\x* wakaparadzira\x + Map. 89.10. 147.16. Eze. 6.5.\x*\x + Map. 141.7.\x* mapfupa eanokudzikirai musasa\x + Map. 141.7.\x*; maka\add va\add*nyadzisa; nokuti Mwari wakavazvidza.
\p
\v 6 Dai ruponeso rukuru rwaIsraeri rwaibva paZiyoni! Mwari paanodzosa utapwa hwevanhu vake, Jakove achafara, Israeri achapembera.